This paper is about generating natural language text to explain the relationship between scientific documents, which involves document understanding and reasoning. This task is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE).
